	<description>
        <![CDATA[
          <div style="line-height:24px; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px; color:#5b5b5b">JUX Coming Soon plugin allows you to easily create and customize your Joomla Coming Soon page.</div>
          <div style="line-height:24px; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px;color:#5b5b5b">This page can be used for an under-construction website or an under-maintenance website. You will also be able to choose displaying the Login page, About us page, Contact us page or not. All in one page style with smoothly effect!</div>
          <div style="line-height:24px; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px;color:#5b5b5b">This plugin works with Joomla 2.5.x and Joomla 3.x</div>
          <div style="line-height:24px; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px;color:#5b5b5b">This plugin support Beautiful countdown effects, background image, background slideshow and background video from Youtube. <b>Note:</b> Video don't display on Mobile devices!</div>
          <div style="line-height:24px; font-weight:normal; font-size:13px;color:#5b5b5b">With JUX Coming Soon plugin, the Coming soon page is responsive and customizable, you'll be able to show or not the information below:</div>
          <ul style="color:#5b5b5b;">
            <li>Logo</li>
            <li>Homepage</li>
            <li>About us page</li>
            <li>Contact us page</li>
            <li>Login page</li>
            <li>Favicon</li>
            <li>Background Style: Image, Video, Slideshow</li>
            <li>Adress and Map</li>
            <li>Subscribe Mail</li>
            <li>Social networks</li>
            <li>Countdown</li>
            <li>Meta tags data</li>
            <li>Logon rights to user groups</li>
          </ul>
          <div style="font-weight:bold;">
            To activate the offline page, just activate our plugin.<br> 
            </div>
          ]]>   
    </description>
